---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Platform | C-Mind">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>The C-Mind Platform</h1>
    <p class="muted" style="max-width: 720px;">
      The C-Mind platform uses carefully governed artificial intelligence to
      support mental health engagement while prioritizing safety, transparency,
      and clinical alignment.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p style="max-width: 720px;">
      The platform is designed to deliver structured, evidence-informed interactions
      that adapt to user needs over time, while maintaining clear boundaries
      regarding diagnosis and treatment.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Deployment & Integration</h2>
    <p style="max-width: 720px;">
      C-Mind is intended for use in research, pilot, and care-support settings,
      with configurations that allow integration into existing workflows when
      appropriate.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
